f using) and serve immediately."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Chocolate mixture may appear curdled in step 3, but continue with recipe as it will mix together when grated chocolate is added in step 4.","Fold egg whites into chocolate mixture immediately to avoid egg whites deflating.","Delicious served with orange sorbet."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","45m","4 portions"]}